{"tid":547095,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"憂中國影響力　澳洲出招收緊外資投資當地能源基建及農田","createTime":"2018-02-01T06:28:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-01T08:31:11.000Z","uid":39464,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e13a9e2749504e988931d8705d9853e79fb04dc9","tid":547095,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T06:28:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/MOR-01_aLtYz_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FMOR-01_aLtYz_1200x0.png&h=171c44e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於擔心中國對當地政商界的影響力，澳洲政府公布收緊關鍵能源基建和農田的外國投資審查，賦予交易審查機構可以基於國家安全考慮而設限。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲財長Scott Morrison表示，將賦予外國投資審查委員會(Foreign Investment Review Board)審查所有涉及能源資產出售交易的權限，以限制外國公司對澳洲輸電網絡的掌控。Morrison表示，今後所有向外國買家出售輸配電資產和部份發電資產的申請，都將受到擁有權限制或其他條件約束。<br />\n<br />\n同時，任何優質農田的出售，都要讓本地農業企業有優先購買權，並且要把交易先廣傳至少30天，並且要在購入後5年內發展土地，以防囤地。<br />\n<br />\n年半前，Morrison先後否決了中國內地企業和香港長江基建對該國畜牧巨頭S.Kidman &amp; Co Ltd.以及電網企業AusGrid的收購交易 。<br />\n<br />\n此前中國對澳洲農場和能源網絡的投資在該國引發爭議，而澳洲國內對來自​​中國和其他國家的政治干預也越發警惕。<br />\n<br />\n同時，今日公布的選舉申報亦顯示，與中國有聯繫的商人在2016選舉前向政黨作出數以十萬計美元的政治捐款。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/憂中國影響力-澳洲收緊審批外資投資當地能源基建及農田/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E6%86%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E5%8A%9B-%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E6%94%B6%E7%B7%8A%E5%AF%A9%E6%89%B9%E5%A4%96%E8%B3%87%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E7%95%B6%E5%9C%B0%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90%E5%9F%BA%E5%BB%BA%E5%8F%8A%E8%BE%B2%E7%94%B0%2F&d=tKULNKj27C%2FG92dllZ2ZRL5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=19c43a17\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E6%86%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E5%8A%9B-%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E6%94%B6%E7%B7%8A%E5%AF%A9%E6%89%B9%E5%A4%96%E8%B3%87%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E7%95%B6%E5%9C%B0%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90%E5%9F%BA%E5%BB%BA%E5%8F%8A%E8%BE%B2%E7%94%B0%2F&h=ac12c721\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/憂中國影響力-澳洲收緊審批外資投資當地能源基建及農田/</a>"},{"pid":"886b838d495044fccbe8c105557c6eafa7863c23","tid":547095,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T06:50:52.000Z","msg":"太遲啦戇鳩, FIRB 又係垃圾"},{"pid":"201cec2c18ec8d6937e094a50ecf015d5c0c94f4","tid":547095,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T06:51:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8ef4159c7c71412f2e5072042dc5f92754954208","tid":547095,"uid":60281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"201cec2c18ec8d6937e094a50ecf015d5c0c94f4","tid":547095,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T06:51:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T06:52:45.000Z","msg":"係班鬼佬後知後覺，一直無防避，而家先發現有問題"},{"pid":"464efddda076788271084a91a3282268d1cd9688","tid":547095,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T06:53:29.000Z","msg":"誠哥都瀨野"},{"pid":"41de6245bb4e06edd511fdae055f7e3ae08dd2a5","tid":547095,"uid":127988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"464efddda076788271084a91a3282268d1cd9688","tid":547095,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T06:53:29.000Z","msg":"誠哥都瀨野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T07:04:59.000Z","msg":"誠哥:我同事頭婆都有d 交情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b44affc6eb83e05cce6f8684d7f87054b07d7c7b","tid":547095,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T08:22:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"270ec7f9641a8eced64ae4c00f13fbf4ee885ece","tid":547095,"uid":110019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T08:31:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>誠哥都瀨野</blockquote><br />\n奶共係要付出代價既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}